name: Celtics
summary: The Boston Celtics and Cleveland Cavaliers are set to face off in the second round of the 2024 NBA playoffs. The Celtics won Game 1 of the series 120-95, while the Cavaliers won Game 2 106-93. Jaylen Brown and Derrick White led the Celtics' offense in Game 1, while Darius Garland led the Cavaliers' offense in Game 2. The Celtics are considered the favorites to win the series, but the Cavaliers have shown that they can compete with them. The two teams are scheduled to meet again in Game 3 on May 13th.

name: Bruins
summary: In the ongoing NHL playoffs, the Boston Bruins and Florida Panthers have engaged in a heated rivalry. After the Bruins survived a Game 7 scare in the first round, they now face the Panthers in the second round. The Panthers have already emerged victorious in Game 1 and Game 2 of the series, setting the stage for a pivotal Game 3. Fans will eagerly tune in to watch the continuation of this intense matchup as the Bruins seek revenge for their recent losses and the Panthers aim to extend their dominance.
